{"tid":1901054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［屌你老母］未來數年預算赤字　繼續爭「明日大嶼」研究5億撥款　黃緯倫：盼社會放開懷抱 畀個機會","createTime":"2020-02-27T14:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T14:59:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"539ecfcfdf9a64f97055508da4785a7380591349","tid":1901054,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:58:15.000Z","msg":"估算耗資逾 6000 億元的明日大嶼計劃，在最新發表的《財政預算案》中亦有提及，政府指希望在下個財政年度盡快爭取撥款，開展「明日大嶼」的工程、規劃和財務評估等相關研究。發展局局長黃緯倫今天表示，自己尊重外間對計劃耗資的質疑，但盼望社會對明日大嶼「畀個機會」，讓填海計劃的前期研究能早日開展，<br />\n⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%95%B8%E5%B9%B4%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E8%B5%A4%E5%AD%97-%E7%BA%8C%E7%88%AD-%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B6%BC-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE-%E9%BB%83%E7%B7%AF%E5%80%AB-%E7%9B%BC%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E7%95%80%E5%80%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%2588%25AD-%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E7%25B7%25AF%25E5%2580%25AB-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2595%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0SUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=da23ca1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E8%25B5%25A4%25E5%25AD%2597-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%2588%25AD-%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B6%25BC-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E7%25B7%25AF%25E5%2580%25AB-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2595%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=905292aa\" target